nodes.text: Fleek eels were a species of eel with gray skin, a defined dorsal ridge and a pink, fleshy opening to their buccal tunnel. They could be found in the oceans of the planet Corellia and were caught by the fishermen of Coronet City, where they were a staple of the city's fishmarkets.

A fleek eel first appeared in the 2018 film Solo: A Star Wars Story, and was identified in the accompanying reference book Solo: A Star Wars Story The Official Guide, written by Pablo Hidalgo. In Star Wars Legends, Fleek eels first appeared in the 1996 Shadows of the Empire novel written by Steve Perry.
